Here is a Java function that calculates the final distance traveled:

```
public double calcDistance(double force, double angle, double weight) {
    double radians = Math.toRadians(angle);
    double acceleration = force / weight;
    double time = Math.sqrt((2 * weight * Math.sin(radians)) / acceleration);
    double distance = (force / weight) * Math.pow(time, 2);
    return distance;
}
```

